Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That kid got on my bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:14.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His cap was pulled down low and he smelled like lemons, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it, he's a runaway, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it, he's a runaway, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We, uh, don't know if he did yet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:25.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well you see, when kids get on the bus, they usually look out the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but... that kid sat in the back of the bus
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he looked like he was worried about something
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he just stared straight ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:35.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and it looked like he might be hiding from something
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fe looked worried
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like he was hiding...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup, I was right... that Mitsuhiko's run away from home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:45.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:48.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And do you remember where he got off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, let me think...\NI'm pretty sure it was Beika Station
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? A«boy thatesmelledslikeslemons?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a cap on and he was carrying a backpack
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I think I know which kid they're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, he bought an adult ticket by mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... he was in a rush and wanted us to exchange it right away, that.one...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was in a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he was really excited- like somebody was after him or something
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know where he was heading...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm:... let's see
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it was an adult ticket for 1.900 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so... it'd probably be to the Chiba area...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:37.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or maybe Gunma
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's NO use
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody who works here's seen him
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means he might have transferred to another line somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our last hope
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that boy passed through here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're-a small station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have those automatic ticket gates like in the big city
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:21.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I'd notice any Kid that acted as sfépicious as him
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was the last to get off and then he hid behind the station building
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but right after that, he ran off towards the mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:33.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phew, I don't believe it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we got this far on only these clues, he smelled like lemons,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wore a cap and was carrying a backpack
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the sun's starting to go down too
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing around here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,how are we gonna find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we've got this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, it's located the signal from\NMitsuhikds detective badge
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he's around here for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he's got his badge with him then all we've got to do is radio him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:12.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to but he doesn't answer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:18.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh well, we can find him by tracking him with those tracking glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it bother you though?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko always does everything by the book and he's super careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why do you think he went off into the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,without discussing it with us first
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's running away from home after all
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, don't go jumping to conclusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might be something very innocent
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,like maybe he just fell in love with a girl and he followed her all the way here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:48.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He fell in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It happens and as they saw
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,first love is lemon flavored
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! Let's go guys
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:01.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've gotta find him before it gets dark
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait for me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like he's some place in this forest
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:30.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he still not answering?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eah I'm pretty sure he can hear the beep though
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he can hear the beep though
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there's people over there
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go ask them if they've seen Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait 8 minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go, you kids stay here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:53.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,hey, come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They may be dangerous people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! You guys over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Yamamura of the\NGunma Prefecture Police
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatygs this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the boy with. Mouri's agency...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing in a place like this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh, what do you mean... by the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello there!" pant, pant...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not safe for you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want all unauthorized people out of this forest right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:39.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not safe!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has a bear been sighted?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:45.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man much, much more dangerous than a bear is hiding out around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:48.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't, say this out loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:55.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems a veteran cop let him get away during inspection of the crime scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.01,0:15:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's that serial killer... Kiichiro Numabuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Are you serious!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I don't believe it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:16.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy I ran into in Osaka\NIS here in this forest
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:43.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you've got to leave right now
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:45.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But one of their friends is in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry Conan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry Conan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to let\NMitsuhiko know about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko, why aren't you answering...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a boy somewhere in here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:23.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the same forest a murderer is hiding out in!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you keep a closer eye on him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You brought them here, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:32.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That idiot Mitsuhiko came here on his own without telling us about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we asked all the people working at the train stations if they saw him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.11,0:16:42.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that's how we ended up here in Gunma Prefecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we tracked him with the detective badge he has on,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:48.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that's why we came to this forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:51.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We used my tracking glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Detective badges and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,tracking glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:17:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,aha... my parents bought me those when I was a kid too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in the detective kit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U's got 2 magic pen, words you write it with it disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then there's the magic card where smoke appears when you rub it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then there's the secret paper that disintegrates in water...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One day though
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I started to have my doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't figure out how these things could help in areal investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:24.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want you to go somewhere else and play detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,toys like that aren't dependable,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:28.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you don't know for sure if your friend is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't understand, we're not playing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honest, we're telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko really is around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you're insisting so strongly, show me some proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see those so called tracking glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, just push the button on the frames like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The batteries are dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew, they re just ordinary glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, the batteries are dead, that's all
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:17:59.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:01.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Yamamura! What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Comeron, we're going to go look for Numabucht!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, but these kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Numabuchi got away because you took your eyes off him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd better find him and fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, uh, sir that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:21.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just take those kids to a safe place then join the manhunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:23.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes sir! Right away sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:27.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he's the one who left Numabuchi alone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and went to relieve himself behind the bushes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought he was with the prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that's why I wasn't paying close attention to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means it actually was your fault he escaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess... you could say that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:48.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:53.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come out, come out wherever you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:01.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to keep this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kid's probably already back home by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You kids go on home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:07.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When it gets dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,even someone who knows these woods very well like me, could get lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of the dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because we've got these!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gee, they sure sell some handy things lately
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't buy these!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doctor Agasa made them for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doctor Agasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Made them for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:28.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, I invented this and made them for the kids
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also made those tracking glasses and that detective badge with the radar
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-Then what you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you told me about a boy wandering around somewhere around here is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were telling you the truth, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we're searching like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:50.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell my superior that back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We told you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:56.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I've got to report this to my superior...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,oh rats...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I left my cellular in the police car...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm done for...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I let the prisoner escape during the crime scene investigation and on top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:12.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't report to my superiors that a child had wandered into the woods...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be discharged,\NI know it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I joined the police because I loved watching detective shows
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I finally got to become a detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe being a detective wasn't right for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm just not cut out for this job...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:33.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's okay, you don't have to cheer me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you solved a lot of cases before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's the Yoshifusa Yabuuchi case
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then the lawyer's case in Karuizawa
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the Kashiragami Forest case too
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you did a fantastic job on all those cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan, is all that true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:53.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, it was either me or my dad that really solved them though...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed you had a wide forehead and look intelligent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the intelligent cop type
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.31,0:21:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw gee, you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now Detective Yamamura!\NLet's get back to our search!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know these woods better than anybody, we're counting on you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doctor Agasa from now I want you to call me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yama. I'd appreciate that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he's been watching too many detective shows
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:42.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's beeping again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew they'd come look for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:54.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if I take it off now and talk to them... all my effort would be in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:22:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.68,0:23:50.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe Numabuchi's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.65,0:23:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now see here An!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.31,0:23:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not completely unthinkable though,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:24:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he's a cold blooded killer and he's been hiding out here for 3 whole days
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.39,0:24:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.26,0:24:03.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.66,0:24:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you can hear my voice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.36,0:24:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.43,0:24:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not safe in this forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.50,0:24:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a dangerous killer hiding out around here!
